Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:15.490 --> 00:00:22.869
 OX Crisps is a pièce de résistance in times of conscious cooking. 

00:00:22.869 --> 00:00:31.291
 A proud and self-conscious création that incorporates almost everything within the animal kingdom. 

00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:45.000
 The protein mix is ​​an animal defile of variety and personality. 

00:00:50.500 --> 00:00:57.500
 The march of the hearts dictates the course of each portion, in presence and texture. 

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:10.710
 Mayonnaise is ubiquitous and plays a key role. It lands and unites the animals as an ambitious 

00:01:10.710 --> 00:01:12.340
 Ark of Noah. 

00:01:13.100 --> 00:01:17.100
 The chicken fuses with the inputs of calabrese and bacon 

00:01:18.100 --> 00:01:20.859
 And it accelerates the heart rate. 

00:01:22.100 --> 00:01:25.900
 Like an animal caffeine. 

00:01:28.100 --> 00:01:34.009
 The dance of the grains is lost in the primordial soup of animal fat, 

00:01:34.009 --> 00:01:39.000
 diluting and losing any texture between the teeth. 

00:01:40.939 --> 00:01:47.710
 The attempt to incorporate straw potatoes into the mélange also falls to the ground. 

00:01:47.710 --> 00:01:55.100
 The corrosive force of the profusion of mayonnaise rehydrates and dissolves the drier ingredients. 

00:01:58.810 --> 00:02:06.100
 Its construction reflects the schizophrenia of the food chain mixing predator and prey. 

00:02:12.100 --> 00:02:17.300
 The result is an abrasive proposal of animal picks. 

00:02:18.700 --> 00:02:22.900
 It instigates and cushions the palate. 

00:02:24.100 --> 00:02:29.500
 The excessive liquidity of mayonnaise reduces the personality of the ingredients 

00:02:29.600 --> 00:02:34.800
 creating a palatable denominator of the filo chordata. 

